Generate Students Courses Submission File

Source: R/students_courses.R
generate_student_course_submission_file.Rd

Generate Students Courses Submission File

Usage

generate_student_course_submission_file(
  input_df = usheUtils::fake_student_course_df,
  with_intermediates = FALSE
)

Arguments

input_df

A Data Frame. Must contain the following data fields: (subject_code, course_number, section_number, attempted_credits, earned_credits, course_level_id, final_grade, student_type_code, budget_code, is_concurrent_course, student_id, ssn, course_reference_number).

with_intermediates

Boolean: Option to include intermediate calculated fields.

Value

A Data Frame, with all of the USHE elements required for upload submission. This will also include intermediate values, used to calculate USHE data elements, if option is set.

Examples

generate_student_course_submission_file()
